import React from 'react'
import {Form, Label, FormText, FormGroup, Input,  Button} from "reactstrap"

const FormElements = () =>  {
    return (
        <Form>
                    <FormGroup>
        <FormText color="light">
                Share your short impression
        </FormText>
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="creator">Creator</Label>
        <Input type="text" name="email" id="creator" placeholder="with a placeholder" />
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="title">Title</Label>
        <Input type="text" name="title" id="title" placeholder="password placeholder" />
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="title">message</Label>
        <Input type="text" name="title" id="message" placeholder="password placeholder" />
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="title">Tags</Label>
        <Input type="text" name="title" id="tags" placeholder="password placeholder" />
      </FormGroup>
      <FormGroup>
        <Label for="">Text Area</Label>
        <Input type="textarea" name="text" id="exampleText" />
      </FormGroup>
      <Button type="submit">Submit</Button>
    </Form>
    )
}

export default FormElements
